fields.name: Avidity Signature Strapback Hat
fields.description: Introducing the Avidity Signature Strapback Hat: a sleek, all-black cap that combines style and sophistication. This premium accessory features an embossed Avidity logo in striking white, adding a touch of elegance to its minimalist design.
